DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
1346::$$$message_0012_0000_0000$$$::I haven't thanked Sakura for cooking dinner yet, so I should talk to Sakura.::
1347::$$$message_0012_0001_0000$$$::"It's getting late, so I should walk her home."::
1348::$$$message_0012_0002_0000$$$::Sakura just finished cleaning up, and she's in the living room getting ready to go home.[lr]::
1349::$$$message_0012_0002_0001$$$::"Oh, Senpai. I thought you were taking your bath."[lr]::
1350::$$$message_0012_0002_0002$$$::"I'll take my bath later, after I walk you home."::
1351::$$$message_0012_0003_0000$$$::"Eh? You're going to walk...me home?"[lr]::
1352::$$$message_0012_0003_0001$$$::"Yeah. It's been dangerous at night lately so I'll walk you home. Your house is a pretty long walk, so let me at least do this, since you go out of your way to come here."::
1353::$$$message_0012_0004_0000$$$::"..."[lr]::
1354::$$$message_0012_0004_0001$$$::Sakura purses her lips awkwardly.[lr]::
1355::$$$message_0012_0004_0002$$$::...Did I say something wrong?::
1356::$$$message_0012_0005_0000$$$::"I'm sorry. I appreciate your concern, but you should rest. I know my way home from here, and I should be fine alone."[lr]::
1357::$$$message_0012_0005_0001$$$::"Maybe so, but it really hasn't been safe recently. I'll walk you home at night for a while."::
1358::$$$message_0012_0006_0000$$$::"...But, well...it will cause trouble for you if my brother sees you."[lr]::
1359::$$$message_0012_0006_0001$$$::"Ah..."::
1360::$$$message_0012_0007_0000$$$::I forgot.[lr]::
1361::$$$message_0012_0007_0001$$$::Sakura's older brother Shinji doesn't really like Sakura coming over to my place.[lr]::
1362::$$$message_0012_0007_0002$$$::He can't say much because Sakura says she goes to Fuji-nee's house, but me taking her home might cause problems.[lr]::
1363::$$$message_0012_0007_0003$$$::I don't care if Shinji accuses me of something I didn't actually do, but I don't want him taking it out on Sakura.::
1364::$$$message_0012_0008_0000$$$::"But it wouldn't be a problem if I only walked you halfway, right? There's no way we'll see Shinji at the intersection."[lr]::
1365::$$$message_0012_0008_0001$$$::"..."::
1366::$$$message_0012_0009_0000$$$::Sakura is uncomfortably silent. [lr]::
1367::$$$message_0012_0009_0001$$$::Knowing Sakura, she probably couldn't even lie about the fact that I walked her home.[lr]::
1368::$$$message_0012_0009_0002$$$::"Hey, then how about[line2]"::
1369::$$$message_0012_0010_0000$$$::"Want me to walk her home?"[lr]::
1370::$$$message_0012_0010_0001$$$::An English teacher wearing tiger stripes suddenly pokes her head through the door.::
1371::$$$message_0012_0011_0000$$$::"That really doesn't fix anything. My concern is that a girl's walking alone at night, so adding another girl would be[line2]"[lr]::
1372::$$$message_0012_0011_0001$$$::...Wait a minute.[lr]::
1373::$$$message_0012_0011_0002$$$::Calling Fuji-nee a girl may be a bit of a misnomer.[lr]::
1374::$$$message_0012_0011_0003$$$::There is a reason Fuji-nee is the teacher in charge of the kyudou club.[lr]::
1375::$$$message_0012_0011_0004$$$::She was trained by Old Man Fujimura in kendo, and her fifth rank designation makes her deadly, literally and figuratively.::
1376::$$$message_0012_0012_0000$$$::"I guess it wouldn't be a problem if you went, Fuji-nee. I bet you could beat the crap out of any perverts who might try to strike."[lr]::
1377::$$$message_0012_0012_0001$$$::"Of course I can. And that's why walking Sakura home is not a problem. Are you good with it, Sakura?"[lr]::
1378::$$$message_0012_0012_0002$$$::Yes. As long as it's okay with you.[lr]::
1379::$$$message_0012_0012_0003$$$::"That settles it. Let's get going. I was just thinking I should go home, too."[lr]::
1380::$$$message_0012_0012_0004$$$::Fuji-nee takes Sakura's hand and starts to leave.::
1381::$$$message_0012_0013_0000$$$::"Oh, hold on a minute, Sakura."[lr]::
1382::$$$message_0012_0013_0001$$$::"What is it, Senpai?"[lr]::
1383::$$$message_0012_0013_0002$$$::"Dinner was good. Thank you."[lr]::
1384::$$$message_0012_0013_0003$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
1385::$$$message_0012_0013_0004$$$::"Of course. As long as you don't mind, I will keep working on my cooking, Senpai."[lr]::
1386::$$$message_0012_0013_0005$$$::Sakura beams and leaves the living room.::
1387::$$$message_0012_0014_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
1388::$$$message_0012_0014_0001$$$::I can tell my cheeks are burning red.[lr]::
1389::$$$message_0012_0014_0002$$$::Honestly, Sakura takes me by surprise a lot lately. It's...perplexing.[lr]::
1390::$$$message_0012_0014_0003$$$::Time sure flies. Not so long ago, she was just my friend's little sister. Now, I find sometimes I can't quite look away from her.::
1391::$$$message_0012_0015_0000$$$::I'm so pathetic.[lr]::
1392::$$$message_0012_0015_0001$$$::I've always thought of Sakura as being like family, but I can't seem to readily accept this change.::
x